These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, australian
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
2. the australian is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | romance |
| Nationality       | dutch | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, card-games
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, july
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Hobby   | video-games | card-games |
| Birthday      | july     | march  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, game
2 different pets are kept: hamster, snake
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the game-smoker##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Cigar   | bongani | game  |
| Pet   | hamster | snake |

 #################################

 
